# Project: WebPad

Webtoon reader portal application designed for Myanmar readers.

## Stack at a glance

- **React 18.3** + **TypeScript 5.5** (strict mode, project refs)
- **Vite 5** — build tool, dev server
- **Tailwind CSS v4** — CSS-first config (`@theme` in `src/index.css`), `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin
- **ESLint 9** + **Prettier 3** + `prettier-plugin-tailwindcss`
- **Vitest 4** + Testing Library + jsdom + v8 coverage
- **Husky 9** + **lint-staged 15** — git hooks

## Entry points

- `index.html` → `src/main.tsx` → `<App />` (`src/App.tsx`)
- `src/index.css` — Tailwind import + design tokens
- `vite.config.ts` — app build config
- `vitest.config.ts` — test config (separate file because vitest bundles its own vite)

## Top-level commands

```bash
npm run dev          # vite dev server (port 5173)
npm run build        # tsc -b && vite build
npm run preview      # serve production build
npm run lint         # eslint .
npm run lint:fix     # eslint . --fix
npm run format       # prettier --write (src/ + wiki/)
npm run format:check # prettier --check
npm run test         # vitest (watch)
npm run test:run     # vitest run (single)
npm run test:ui      # vitest --ui
npm run check        # lint + format:check + test:run + build  ← runs in pre-push
```

